item.title: Abba Father Let Me Be
item.description: Key: G Galatians 4: 6 Abba Father let me be Yours and Yours alone, May my will forever be, Evermore Your own. Never let my heart grow cold, Never let me go, Abba Father, let me be, Yours and Yours alone.
